cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with dialog systems and natural language processing using recurrent neural networks. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of domain-specific knowledge and templates to improve dialog control. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses supervised and reinforcement learning to optimize the Hybrid Code Networks. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper encodes domain-specific knowledge as software and system action templates. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the performance of customer-facing dialog systems.
